sources.title: Rampart - Full Movie
sources.description:
Woody Harrelson (""True Detective"") stars as Dave Brown, a corrupt cop in LAPD's scandal-ridden Rampart Division, whose life begins to come apart at the seams as a result of his own uncompromising brutality. Also starring Ben Foster, Oscar winner Brie Larson and seven-time Golden Globe nominee Sigourney Weaver.
